Sec. 122.401. PENALTY SCHEDULE. (a) The department by rule
shall adopt a schedule of sanctions and penalties for violations of
this chapter and rules adopted under this chapter that does not
conflict with 7 U.S.C. Section 1639p(e).
(b) A penalty collected under this chapter other than a civil
penalty collected under Subchapter H must be deposited in the state
hemp production account under Section 122.003.
Added by Acts 2019, 86th Leg., R.S., Ch. 764 (H.B. 1325), Sec. 2, eff.
June 10, 2019.

